<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/national-space-operations-centre> <http://schema.org/name> "National Space Operations Centre" .
_:N3737c73b8f374071b949f64bad03cd88 <http://schema.org/itemListElement> _:N5e886d4f021c45ff9b9dbe30177d75f8 .
_:Nc22cf979fdb9485a9c357f8b7e8b14d0 <http://schema.org/text> "We develop and operate the UK’s space surveillance and protection capabilities." .
_:Nc22cf979fdb9485a9c357f8b7e8b14d0 <http://schema.org/publisher> _:Nf025c80426c44a239e0658f319c6443d .
